e&lt;/a&gt; camps in the area, like &lt;a href=\"Mor%27gran%20Logworks\"&gt;Mor'gran Logworks&lt;/a&gt;.\nFly to &lt;a href=\"Joz%27s%20Rylaks\"&gt;Joz's Rylaks&lt;/a&gt; in and run north to the &lt;a href=\"Ring%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Ring of Blood&lt;/a&gt;. Northeast of the ring itself, find three Party Animals dancing behind the &lt;a href=\"Bass%20Blaster\"&gt;Bass Blaster&lt;/a&gt; at The ogres are upset, but won't attack:\nFinally, fly to the &lt;a href=\"Everbloom%20Wilds\"&gt;Everbloom Wilds&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Gorgrond\"&gt;Gorgrond&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Cord%20of%20Ancient%20Wood\"&gt;Cord of Ancient Wood&lt;/a&gt; drops from any &lt;a href=\"Draenor%20ancient\"&gt;Draenor ancient&lt;/a&gt; in the quest area, like a &lt;a href=\"Lumbering%20Ancient\"&gt;Lumbering Ancient&lt;/a&gt;.\nOn complete, the &lt;a href=\"Tune-O-Tron%205000\"&gt;Tune-O-Tron 5000&lt;/a&gt; spawns next to Fix. Open the &lt;a href=\"Stash%20of%20Dusty%20Music%20Rolls\"&gt;Stash of Dusty Music Rolls&lt;/a&gt; to acquire the seven faction racial tunes:\nThere are many more to be found. Biggswrench lists a few hints, which are listed on the &lt;a href=\"Garrison%20Jukebox\"&gt;Garrison Jukebox&lt;/a&gt; article.\nVideos.\n&lt;vplayer /&gt;"}
