\"&gt;Pinchwhistle Gearworks&lt;/a&gt; and run south to &lt;a href=\"Pinchwhistle%20Point\"&gt;Pinchwhistle Point&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Laz-Tron%20Disc%20Reader\"&gt;Laz-Tron Disc Reader&lt;/a&gt; is at on the upper floor of the inn. Looting it will spawn a hostile Spore-addled Goblin.\nFinally, fly to &lt;a href=\"Joz%27s%20Rylaks\"&gt;Joz's Rylaks&lt;/a&gt; in and run north to the &lt;a href=\"Ring%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Ring of Blood&lt;/a&gt;. Northeast of the ring itself, find three Party Animals dancing behind the &lt;a href=\"Bass%20Blaster\"&gt;Bass Blaster&lt;/a&gt; at The ogres are upset, but won't attack:\nOn complete, the &lt;a href=\"Tune-O-Tron%205000\"&gt;Tune-O-Tron 5000&lt;/a&gt; spawns next to Fix. Open the &lt;a href=\"Stash%20of%20Dusty%20Music%20Rolls\"&gt;Stash of Dusty Music Rolls&lt;/a&gt; to acquire the seven faction racial tunes:\nThere are many more to be found. Bassbolter lists a few hints, which are listed on the &lt;a href=\"Garrison%20Jukebox\"&gt;Garrison Jukebox&lt;/a&gt; article.\nVideos.\n&lt;vplayer /&gt;"}
