{"id": "39864", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39864", "title": "Sayoc", "text": "Sayoc was an &lt;a href=\"orc\"&gt;orc&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Arms%20of%20Legend\"&gt;Arms of Legend&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Valley%20of%20Honor\"&gt;Valley of Honor&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Orgrimmar\"&gt;Orgrimmar&lt;/a&gt;.\nHe was a &lt;a href=\"weapon%20master\"&gt;weapon master&lt;/a&gt;, and taught the skill to wield the following:\nQuotes.\nHere to learn how to wield a new weapon, or just here to waste my time?\n&lt;a href=\"Ansekhwa\"&gt;Ansekhwa&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"tauren\"&gt;tauren&lt;/a&gt; weapon master, is on da &lt;a href=\"Thunder%20Bluff\"&gt;Thunder Bluff&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"lower%20rise\"&gt;lower rise&lt;/a&gt;. He can train one and two-handed maces, staves and guns.\n&lt;a href=\"Hanashi\"&gt;Hanashi&lt;/a&gt;, standing next to me here, can instruct in the use of bows, one and two-handed axes, staves and all manner of thrown weapons.\n&lt;a href=\"Archibald\"&gt;Archibald&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Forsaken\"&gt;undead&lt;/a&gt; weapon master in the &lt;a href=\"War%20Quarter\"&gt;War Quarter&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Undercity\"&gt;Undercity&lt;/a&gt;, can teach the use of crossbows, daggers, one and two-handed swords and polearms."}
