{"id": "76011", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=76011", "title": "Library", "text": "A library is a large room or building filled with books.\nIn the RPG.\nA community with a library may be known as a library community. The community has access to a large collection of books, scrolls, and other written material. Scholars and mages are seen coming and going, gathering information to help with their personal research; members of the community educate one another on various topics. Community members are knowledgeable about researching information in the library's archives."}
{"id": "36767", "revid": "4374524", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=36767", "title": "Library (Ironforge)", "text": "The Library is a large hoard of knowledge and artifacts within the &lt;a href=\"Dwarf\"&gt;dwarven&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"capital%20city\"&gt;capital city&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Ironforge\"&gt;Ironforge&lt;/a&gt;. Occupying the eastern section of the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Explorers\"&gt;Hall of Explorers&lt;/a&gt;, the Library is arguably the largest singular building in the city, and is notably also home to a museum and many &lt;a href=\"quest%20giver\"&gt;quest giver&lt;/a&gt;s. The Library and its contents are administered by the &lt;a href=\"Explorers%27%20League\"&gt;Explorers' League&lt;/a&gt;, who are dedicated to collecting knowledge and relics from across &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;. Members of the League catalogue and analyze all of their findings in the library. Before coming to &lt;a href=\"Pandaria\"&gt;Pandaria&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hilda%20Hornswaggle\"&gt;Hilda Hornswaggle&lt;/a&gt; spent five years here.\nThe library being very large, &lt;a href=\"Librarian%20Mae%20Paledust\"&gt;Librarian Mae Paledust&lt;/a&gt; is the best finder to contact to find rare books. A row of coded books is also present at the far end of the library, headed by &lt;a href=\"Bill%20Spearshaker\"&gt;Bill Spearshaker&lt;/a&gt;.\nMuseum.\nPart of the Library is occupied by a large museum, run by &lt;a href=\"Curator%20Thorius\"&gt;Curator Thorius&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe following artifacts are on display:\nBooks.\nCopies of the following readable tomes can be found within the library proper:"}
