{"id": "185427", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=185427", "title": "Ursoc's Den", "text": "Ursoc's Den is the lair of &lt;a href=\"Wild%20God\"&gt;Wild God&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Ursoc\"&gt;Ursoc&lt;/a&gt; who once battled the &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Legion\"&gt;Burning Legion&lt;/a&gt; during the &lt;a href=\"War%20of%20the%20Ancients\"&gt;War of the Ancients&lt;/a&gt;. It is located northwest of &lt;a href=\"Westfall%20Brigade%20Encampment\"&gt;Westfall Brigade Encampment&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Grizzly%20Hills\"&gt;Grizzly Hills&lt;/a&gt;. The den is a great bear's head that has been carved out of solid rock, the mouth of it leading into a natural canyon. It is here that Ursoc dwelled thousands of years ago. \nHistory.\nWrath of the Lich King.\nAt the time of the &lt;a href=\"war%20against%20the%20Lich%20King\"&gt;war against the Lich King&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"furbolg\"&gt;furbolg&lt;/a&gt;s of &lt;a href=\"Grizzlemaw\"&gt;Grizzlemaw&lt;/a&gt;, feeling the clutch of madness, attempted to resurrect the spirit of Ursoc. However, the corruption of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Yogg-Saron\"&gt;Yogg-Saron&lt;/a&gt; tainted him as well, until a shaman of the &lt;a href=\"Timbermaw%20tribe\"&gt;Timbermaw tribe&lt;/a&gt; named &lt;a href=\"Tur%20Ragepaw\"&gt;Tur Ragepaw&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s came to cleanse the corruption in the den, freeing the spirit of the Wild God.\nLegion.\nDuring the &lt;a href=\"third%20invasion%20of%20the%20Burning%20Legion\"&gt;third invasion of the Burning Legion&lt;/a&gt;, a dream portal opened up within a tree downhill from the Den, allowing druids exclusive access to the &lt;a href=\"Emerald%20Dreamway\"&gt;Emerald Dreamway&lt;/a&gt;. At some point, Guardian druids visited &lt;a href=\"Ursoc%27s%20Lair\"&gt;the Den's counterpart&lt;/a&gt; within the Emerald Dream to claim the &lt;a href=\"Claws%20of%20Ursoc\"&gt;Claws of Ursoc&lt;/a&gt;.\nAfter the Wild God was captured by &lt;a href=\"Xavius\"&gt;Xavius&lt;/a&gt;, the heroes confronted &lt;a href=\"Ursoc%20%28tactics%29\"&gt;a mad and corrupted Ursoc&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ursoc%27s%20Lair\"&gt;the Den's counterpart&lt;/a&gt; corrupted by the &lt;a href=\"Emerald%20Nightmare\"&gt;Emerald Nightmare&lt;/a&gt;."}
