{"id": "511762", "revid": "49740203", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=511762", "title": "Use the Force(s)", "text": "Use the Force(s) is an achievement earned by completing the &lt;a href=\"Cenarius%20%28tactics%29\"&gt;Cenarius&lt;/a&gt; encounter in the &lt;a href=\"Emerald%20Nightmare%20%28instance%29\"&gt;Emerald Nightmare&lt;/a&gt; instance without cleansing the adds which spawn during the fight, on Normal difficulty or higher. \nDuring the encounter, Cenarius will summon adds in the form of &lt;a href=\"dryad\"&gt;dryad&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"treant\"&gt;treant&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"wisp\"&gt;wisp&lt;/a&gt;s, and &lt;a href=\"drake\"&gt;drake&lt;/a&gt;s. Any of these adds may be cleansed during the fight through &lt;a href=\"Malfurion%20Stormrage\"&gt;Malfurion Stormrage&lt;/a&gt;'s Cleansing Ground ability that he casts, which will transform them into Allies of Nature that can aid the raid group. To obtain the achievement, ensure that none of these adds are cleansed before defeating Cenarius."}
