{"id": "170290", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=170290", "title": "Raise Dead (death knight ability)", "text": "Raise Dead is a &lt;a href=\"Death%20knight\"&gt;Death knight&lt;/a&gt; talent that allows the death knight to raise a &lt;a href=\"Risen%20Ally\"&gt;Risen Ally&lt;/a&gt; as a temporary &lt;a href=\"combat%20pet\"&gt;combat pet&lt;/a&gt;. It is automatically learned by Unholy death knights. Unholy death knights can also upgrade the ghoul to a permanent pet with a shorter cooldown with the &lt;a href=\"Raise%20Dead%20%28Unholy%29\"&gt;Raise Dead (Unholy)&lt;/a&gt; talent.\nBackground.\n&lt;a href=\"Raise%20Dead\"&gt;Raise Dead&lt;/a&gt; and other similar abilities have been a staple of the Warcraft series, commonly used by practitioners of &lt;a href=\"necromancy\"&gt;necromancy&lt;/a&gt;, including &lt;a href=\"Necrolyte%20%28Warcraft%20I%29\"&gt;Necrolyte&lt;/a&gt; units in \"&lt;a href=\"Warcraft%20I\"&gt;Warcraft I&lt;/a&gt;\", &lt;a href=\"Death%20Knight%20%28Warcraft%20II%29\"&gt;Death Knight&lt;/a&gt; units in \"&lt;a href=\"Warcraft%20II\"&gt;Warcraft II&lt;/a&gt;\", and &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20%28Warcraft%20III%29\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; units in \"&lt;a href=\"Warcraft%20III\"&gt;Warcraft III&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
