{"id": "179725", "revid": "819614", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=179725", "title": "Raise Some Hell", "text": "\"Raise Some Hell\" is the fifth song by &lt;a href=\"Level%2080%20Elite%20Tauren%20Chieftain\"&gt;Level 80 Elite Tauren Chieftain&lt;/a&gt;, which made its live debut on June 29, 2008 at the &lt;a href=\"Worldwide%20Invitational%232008\"&gt;Worldwide Invitational&lt;/a&gt; in Paris, France. It was written about the glorification of Diablo, the primary antagonist of the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20franchise\"&gt;Diablo universe&lt;/a&gt;, to celebrate &lt;a href=\"Blizzard%20Entertainment\"&gt;Blizzard&lt;/a&gt;'s newly announced development of Diablo III. It is uncertain if the band will record a studio version of the song."}
